white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.4pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><SPAN \nlang=EN-US style=\"COLOR: black\"><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" \nsize=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal \nstyle=\"BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.4pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><FONT \nsize=3><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"><SPAN lang=EN-GB \nstyle=\"mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">I own three buildings in Foch area in Paris, \nhaving a total surface of </SPAN><st1:metricconverter \nProductID=\"1,780 square meters\"><SPAN lang=EN-GB \nstyle=\"mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">1,780 square \nmeters</SPAN></st1:metricconverter><SPAN lang=EN-GB \nstyle=\"mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">, evaluated to an amount of 25 millions euros \nthat I am ready to</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"COLOR: black\"> put in guarantee \nagainst a loan amounting to 4 millions euros, because this 4 millions euros \nwould resolve the situation and would let you all the necessary time to take \nyour decision to become a partner or not.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT \nface=\"Times New Roman\" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT \nface=\"Times New Roman\" size=3>Very truly yours,</FONT></SPAN></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT \nface=\"Times New Roman\" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT \nface=\"Times New Roman\" size=3>Armand Azoulay</FONT></SPAN></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT \nsize=3><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">+ 33 6 22 52 07 \n01<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P></FONT></DIV></BODY></HTML>\n","is_from_epstein":false,"attachments":0,"avatar_color":"#db4437","stars":9,"is_redacted":false}]